himachi_suisei_to_perform_at_aso_rock_festival_2023_first_outdoor_fes_appearance_by_hololive_talents" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/vtuber_hoshimachi_suisei_to_perform_at_aso_rock_festival_2023_first_outdoor_fes_appearance_by_hololive_talents.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/vtuber_hoshimachi_suisei_to_perform_at_aso_rock_festival_2023_first_outdoor_fes_appearance_by_hololive_talents.jpg" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="677" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/vtuber_hoshimachi_suisei_to_perform_at_aso_rock_festival_2023_first_outdoor_fes_appearance_by_hololive_talents.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-96894"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：推特<br>© 2023 年阿苏摇滚音乐节火。<br> © 2016 COVER 公司</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>星町水成将成为第一个出现在 VTuber 办公室 Hololive Production 旗下日本女子组合“Holo Live”户外音乐节的艺人。</p><p> “ASO ROCK FESTIVAL FIRE 2023”是在熊本县南阿苏村的熊本露天剧场 Aspecta 举办的户外摇滚音乐节。 Suisei Hoshimachi预计将于9月30日亮相，Ulfuls、Kyary Pamyu Pamyu、小泉恭子、Sambomaster等其他著名艺人也预定亮相。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/suisei_hosimati/status/1681939231969775618" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc9WCNtgOJKCG6m7ZJJPVxl0hzierAmzlAJW-zpK-lGSmwR8bIVNR7xaNmAeW3s5EXMSpJfORgErlDjiV6uCEEIFZCFLuXDe8Ef4Ftey_HkYt5XqN-M1OAdx4cuNgOddD-D3JvmUahe9w5YtRIO7PE4L=w1097-h806-s-no" alt=""/></a> </figure><p></p><div class="vjepe64b95e0d05892" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
